title: n8n AI 101 course
learningObjectives: Understand the basics of Artificial Intelligence
Learn about Machine Learning and Deep Learning
Gain knowledge about AI tools and applications
Apply AI concepts to real world problems

finalProjectDetails.overview: The final project requires students to apply all the knowledge gained throughout the course to solve a real-world problem using AI.
finalProjectDetails.submissionInstructions: Submit the final project report with detailed description about the machine learning model, implementation process, results, and learning outcomes.
